There was one other sighting in Wenatchee on or around October 22nd 2013
Summary: Wife noticed object hovering and moving around back and forth
divs: Sighting DetailsWhile my wife was watching the kids at the bus stop she noticed this object hovering at high altitude and sort of bouncing around. It didn't make noise that she could hear and was moving quickly when moved. After a few minutes it just seemed to disappear. She felt shocked and a little confused on what she was seeing. She quickly grabbed the camera and took a couple of pictures.
